View of Europe

# Europe
df %>% filter(independence %in% c('Yes', 'No'),
                            view_europe <= 10) %>%
  group_by(independence) %>%
  summarise(avg = mean(view_europe),
            med = median(view_europe))
# A tibble: 2 x 3
  independence   avg   med
  <fct>        <dbl> <dbl>
1 Yes           3.92  4.00
2 No            5.22  5.00
